CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 4, 2014

[Cite as 03104/2014 Case Announcements #3, 2014-Ohio-805.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2014-0251. Ibrahim v. Ibrahim.

Franklin App. No. 13AP-681, 2013-Ohio-5401. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

Upon consideration of appellant’s emergency motion for stay, it is ordered by the court that appellee shall file a response, if any, no later than 10:00 a.m. on Thursday, March 6, 2014.
